  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the effect of the International Child Development
      Program (ICDP). Research questions to be answered:

        1. Does the ICDP affect children's psychosocial functioning compared to treatment as usual?

        2. Does the ICDP change parent-child interaction?
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
